  "text": "Neutrophil Migration. Neutrophil migration was performed as described previously [CITATION_1] . In brief, peritoneal lavage fluids were harvested and total cell counts were performed using a Coulter ACT series cell counter. Differential cell counts were carried out on cytocentrifuge slides (Cytospin 3; Shandon Southern Products) stained by the May-Grü nwald-Giemsa method.",
